  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You finally open your eyes after a memory that seems to go back forever.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After fulfilling a few orders, you realize that you're trapped in a crazy chef's simulation. <strong>Bake all the requested cakes before he catches you</strong>…</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the factory to <strong>find out how you got there</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must find a way to escape, complete all <strong><u>7 unique orders</u></strong> while you can and <strong><u>discover the two endings</u></strong>. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665040/extras/23999e3abd0f45460c6d5426a2fdfc92.poster.avif?t=1772832693\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665040/extras/23999e3abd0f45460c6d5426a2fdfc92.webm?t=1772832693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665040/extras/23999e3abd0f45460c6d5426a2fdfc92.mp4?t=1772832693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You're on your own for the first few orders</strong>, but after that, <u><strong>the chef is behind you</strong></u>, getting closer and closer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The longer you wait, the faster he walks. Finish cakes to push him back.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover the other gameplay mechanics as you play!</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665040/extras/90cba58b75bf1e2a8b52f2e3a70848a1.poster.avif?t=1772832693\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665040/extras/90cba58b75bf1e2a8b52f2e3a70848a1.webm?t=1772832693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665040/extras/90cba58b75bf1e2a8b52f2e3a70848a1.mp4?t=1772832693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Safe orders:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You can play The OG Cake Factory without worrying about the chef</strong> with the safe orders (which include 4 difficulty levels).</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You finally open your eyes after a memory that seems to go back forever.</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After fulfilling a few orders, you realize that you're trapped in a crazy chef's simulation. <strong>Bake all the requested cakes before he catches you</strong>…</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the factory to <strong>find out how you got there</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must find a way to escape, complete all <strong><u>7 unique orders</u></strong> while you can and <strong><u>discover the two endings</u></strong>. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665040/extras/23999e3abd0f45460c6d5426a2fdfc92.poster.avif?t=1772832693\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665040/extras/23999e3abd0f45460c6d5426a2fdfc92.webm?t=1772832693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665040/extras/23999e3abd0f45460c6d5426a2fdfc92.mp4?t=1772832693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You're on your own for the first few orders</strong>, but after that, <u><strong>the chef is behind you</strong></u>, getting closer and closer.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The longer you wait, the faster he walks. Finish cakes to push him back.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover the other gameplay mechanics as you play!</strong></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2665040/extras/90cba58b75bf1e2a8b52f2e3a70848a1.poster.